      "author": "Fahad_S (Fahad Sheji)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>I’m having trouble using the “Get Item by Column Value” action on Zapier to retrieve the date columns “Visit Start” and “Visit End”. These columns are present in <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>, but Zapier is not displaying them as options.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/b/cb61bf7a0bd4e6d0aa602f1555334ba99632085b.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/c/b/cb61bf7a0bd4e6d0aa602f1555334ba99632085b_2_604x499.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"604\" height=\"499\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">854×706 38.3 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><em>Screenshot of the column on <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> board</em><br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/a/7a7d4ca53223538e48247997abd1423e6c5e7ec8.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/a/7a7d4ca53223538e48247997abd1423e6c5e7ec8_2_690x302.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"302\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1294×567 46 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><em>this is what I see when I click on the column settings</em><br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/4/84a6d8ed2750a50940f3a153c818757c5ad49ccb.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/4/84a6d8ed2750a50940f3a153c818757c5ad49ccb_2_690x356.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"356\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1490×769 89.6 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Does anyone know why those specific columns are not showing in Zapier?</p>"
    },
